    <detaileddescription>
<para>in the most general form, geodesic path can start in any mesh location (<ref refid="structMR_1_1MeshTriPoint" kindref="compound">MeshTriPoint</ref>), then pass triangles along straight lines, making turns on edges (MeshEdgePoint), and finish in any mesh location (<ref refid="structMR_1_1MeshTriPoint" kindref="compound">MeshTriPoint</ref>) </para>
    </detaileddescription>
